A cyberpunk-style illustration of a glowing tropical island city at night, viewed from above, completely wrapped in an intricate web of neon blue and purple wireless signal waves emanating from countless rooftops and towers. The urban landscape features futuristic skyscrapers with holographic advertisements, palm trees silhouetted against the electric glow, and streams of data visualized as flowing light particles connecting buildings across the dense metropolis. A large padlock made of pure cyan light floats prominently in the sky above the city, its surface covered in circuit patterns, symbolizing encrypted connection security. The surrounding ocean reflects the city's vibrant glow in deep magenta and teal hues, while rain streaks add atmosphere to the humid tropical night.
